{"tid":2145514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾國衛用Bingo紙回應 唯獨沒有「與有榮焉」奶錫中共春袋","createTime":"2020-08-08T05:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T06:30:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"43a0096d42c61c104a092014be1ee8e17f8f7fac","tid":2145514,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"曾國衛：制裁是自欺欺人毫無意義<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-08-08 13:09<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局長曾國衛批評美國對中港官員的所謂制裁，簡直是<span class=\"gold\">自欺欺人</span>，對他<span class=\"gold\">不痛不癢</span>、<span class=\"gold\">毫無影響</span>、<span class=\"gold\">毫無意義</span>。曾國衛說，對於美國的<span class=\"gold\">霸凌行為</span>、<span class=\"gold\">雙重標準</span>是司空見慣，指美國自稱民主國家，所謂尊重人權，卻公然肆意對人「起底」，簡直是<span class=\"gold\">流氓行徑</span>，但亦符合他們一貫的流氓作風。曾國衛說特區政府不會被美國嚇到，反而更令他們堅信現時所做的事是正確的，為國家安全、為香港繁榮穩定，會繼續致力反對、排除一切破壞國家安全、干擾國家內政的<span class=\"gold\">外部勢力</span>入侵。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2351257&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=acf223ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351257</a>"},{"pid":"fbb7e6a412bd87c8aca8efd358b8866a38784cd7","tid":2145514,"uid":11809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"開咗崑崙銀行戶口未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n層樓係咪大陸幫你供埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回應吓點出糧啦不如？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6540a0e28a05391439e171f10c1cb5492fc6658","tid":2145514,"uid":239392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"堅持到底!"},{"pid":"f1accfe246aa5e41f4db5cb258258151b4515ced","tid":2145514,"uid":239392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbb7e6a412bd87c8aca8efd358b8866a38784cd7","tid":2145514,"uid":11809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco